            <scopecontent id="aspace_fb3016d3a7815f7ee2445750a514d365">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Material for: Listen / John Christie, with text by Erik Satie and translation by Simon Cutts. Circle Press, 1975: A. Dummy book: original copy of the projected publication -- B. Monoprint: "Voices, voices..." -- C. Photo positive: positive of the title label -- D. Prospectus: eight different designs (two copies of "Through Frozen Air..."); front has print from book, reverse has publishing information -- E. Letters from Ron King to John Christie, concerning publication information -- F. Translation: Sports et Divertissements; written by Erik Satie and translated by Simon Cutts; original published in 1914.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c>
