               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Material for: A walk along the shore / John Christie, with text by Kenneth White. Circle Press, 1977: A-J Collages: 10 original silk-screened images from the book (one not used) -- K. Dummy layout: 82 pages with corrections by Ron King -- L. Film positives: 23 designs used to make the photoscreens -- M. Photocopy: A Few Signs In the Sand; Kenneth White. Includes White's notes and corrections -- N. Photocopy: A Walk Along the Shore; Kenneth White. Includes White's corrections -- O. Prospectus: publication information.</p>
            </scopecontent>
